'''Clube Ferroviário de Nampula''' is a [[Mozambique|Mozambican]] [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Nampula]]. They play in the top division in Mozambican football, [[Moçambola]]. Their home stadium is [[Estádio do Nampula]]. From 1993 to 2002, [[Filipe Nhussi]], the current [[President of Mozambique]], served as president of the club.

