{{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = Estadio Olímpico (La Vega) | logo_image = | image = | caption = During a LDF game | location = [[Concepción de la Vega]], [[Dominican Republic]] | coordinates = | broke_ground = | opened = | renovations = 2015-2016 | Capacity = 7,000 | owner = Concepción de la Vega Government | operator = [[Atlético Vega Real]] | surface = grass | tenants = [[Atlético Vega Real]] }}
'''Estadio Olímpico''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Concepción de la Vega]], [[Dominican Republic]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and hosts the home games of Jarabacoa of the [[Liga Dominicana de Fútbol]]. The stadium holds 7,000 spectators.
==Renovations== The terrains was renovated after the [[2015 Liga Dominicana de Fútbol]], and now is up to the requirements of the [[CONCACAF]].
